            <Label Text="C++" FontSize="30" FontAttributes="Bold" HorizontalTextAlignment="Center" />
            <Label Text='C++ is a powerful, general-purpose programming language that extends the C programming language by introducing object-oriented programming (OOP) features. It is widely used in system programming, game development, high-performance applications, embedded systems, and operating systems.

C++ provides direct memory access, making it highly efficient for performance-critical applications. It supports multiple paradigms, including procedural programming, OOP, and generic programming. Popular game engines such as Unreal Engine use C++ due to its speed and control over hardware. It is also extensively used in competitive programming because of its efficiency.' 
                   HorizontalTextAlignment="Center" VerticalTextAlignment="Center" FontSize="16"/>

